cell><tablecell></tablecell></tablerow><tablerow><tablecell rowspan="2">2005</tablecell><tablecell><italics><link><target>Nausica of the Valley of the Wind (film)</target><part>Nausica of the Valley of the Wind</part></link></italics></tablecell><tablecell>Kurotowa (voice)</tablecell><tablecell></tablecell></tablerow><tablerow><tablecell><italics><link><target>Loggerheads (film)</target><part>Loggerheads</part></link></italics></tablecell><tablecell>Rev. Robert Austin</tablecell><tablecell></tablecell></tablerow><tablerow><tablecell>2007</tablecell><tablecell><italics><link><target>The Chosen One (2007 film)</target><part>The Chosen One</part></link></italics></tablecell><tablecell>Zebulon 'Zeb' Kirk</tablecell><tablecell></tablecell></tablerow><tablerow><tablecell>2008</tablecell><tablecell><italics><link><target>My Sassy Girl (2008 film)</target><part>My Sassy Girl</part></link></italics></tablecell><tablecell>Dr. Roark</tablecell><tablecell></tablecell></tablerow><tablerow><tablecell rowspan="2">2009</tablecell><tablecell><italics><link><target>Multiple Sarcasms</target></link></italics></tablecell><tablecell>Larry</tablecell><tablecell></tablecell></tablerow><tablerow><tablecell><italics>My Life in the Single Seat: A Documentary</italics></tablecell><tablecell>Himself</tablecell><tablecell></tablecell></tablerow><tablerow><tablecell>2011</tablecell><tablecell><italics><link><target>Fright Night (2011 film)</target><part>Fright Night</part></link></italics></tablecell><tablecell>&quot;Jay Dee&quot;</tablecell><tablecell>(cameo appearance)</tablecell></tablerow><tablerow><tablecell>2012</tablecell><tablecell><italics><link><target>Safe (2012 film)</target><part>Safe</part></link></italics></tablecell><tablecell>Mayor Danny Tremello</tablecell><tablecell></tablecell></tablerow></table><heading level='3'>Television</heading><table class="wikitable"><tablerow><tablehead>Year</tablehead><tablehead>Title</tablehead><tablehead>Role</tablehead><tablehead>Notes</tablehead